quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,28,"Fa-itha istawayta anta waman maAAakaAAala alfulki faquli alhamdu lillahi allatheenajjana mina alqawmi aththalimeen"
  23,29,"Waqul rabbi anzilnee munzalan mubarakanwaanta khayru almunzileen"
  23,30,"Inna fee thalika laayatinwa-in kunna lamubtaleen"
  23,31,"Thumma ansha/na min baAAdihim qarnan akhareen"
  23,32,"Faarsalna feehim rasoolan minhum anioAAbudoo Allaha ma lakum min ilahin ghayruhuafala tattaqoon"
  23,33,"Waqala almalao min qawmihi allatheenakafaroo wakaththaboo biliqa-i al-akhiratiwaatrafnahum fee alhayati addunyama hatha illa basharun mithlukum ya/kulumimma ta/kuloona minhu wayashrabu mimma tashraboon"
  23,34,"Wala-in ataAAtum basharan mithlakuminnakum ithan lakhasiroon"
  23,35,"AyaAAidukum annakum itha mittumwakuntum turaban waAAithaman annakummukhrajoon"
  23,36,"Hayhata hayhata limatooAAadoon"
  23,37,"In hiya illa hayatunaaddunya namootu wanahya wamanahnu bimabAAootheen"
  23,38,"In huwa illa rajulun iftaraAAala Allahi kathiban wama nahnulahu bimu/mineen"
  23,39,"Qala rabbi onsurnee bimakaththaboon"
  23,40,"Qala AAamma qaleelin layusbihunnanadimeen"
  23,41,"Faakhathat-humu assayhatubilhaqqi fajaAAalnahum ghuthaanfabuAAdan lilqawmi aththalimeen"
  23,42,"Thumma ansha/na min baAAdihimquroonan akhareen"
